---
/**
 * ai-agents · 0005 · Figure 3 — agent state assembled by the runtime into the
 * context window for each stateless LLM call. Verbatim from the source HTML.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 620 188"
        role="img"
        aria-label="The components of agent state assembled by the runtime into the context window for each stateless LLM call"
    >
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <text
                x="150"
                y="16"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="10.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#6b675f"
                letter-spacing=".05em">AGENT STATE (runtime-held)</text
            >
            <rect x="14" y="26" width="130" height="30" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect><text x="79" y="45" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >goal + current task</text
            >
            <rect x="14" y="62" width="130" height="30" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect><text x="79" y="81" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >the plan</text
            >
            <rect x="14" y="98" width="130" height="30" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect><text x="79" y="117" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >message history</text
            >
            <rect x="14" y="134" width="130" height="30" rx="6" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
            ></rect><text x="79" y="153" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#111110"
                >tool outputs / results</text
            >
            <!-- assembler -->
            <line
                x1="144"
                y1="95"
                x2="190"
                y2="95"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <rect
                x="192"
                y="64"
                width="120"
                height="62"
                rx="9"
                fill="#f1eee2"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-width="1.5"></rect>
            <text
                x="252"
                y="90"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">Runtime</text
            >
            <text x="252" y="106" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >assembles context</text
            >
            <line
                x1="312"
                y1="95"
                x2="358"
                y2="95"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <!-- context window -->
            <rect
                x="360"
                y="58"
                width="116"
                height="74"
                rx="9"
                fill="#eef3fb"
                stroke="#1f77d0"
                stroke-width="1.4"></rect>
            <text
                x="418"
                y="88"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="10.5"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#1f77d0">Context</text
            >
            <text x="418" y="104" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#1f77d0"
                >this call only</text
            >
            <line
                x1="476"
                y1="95"
                x2="510"
                y2="95"
                stroke="#6b675f"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <!-- LLM -->
            <rect x="512" y="64" width="96" height="62" rx="9" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"></rect>
            <text
                x="560"
                y="90"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#111110">LLM</text
            >
            <text x="560" y="106" text-anchor="middle" font-size="8.5" fill="#6b675f"
                >stateless</text
            >
            <text x="310" y="180" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#9c968a"
                >Nothing the agent "remembers" exists to the model unless the runtime packs it into <tspan
                    font-style="italic">this</tspan
                > window.</text
            >
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        State lives in the runtime; the context window is just the slice of it the model sees this
        turn. "Memory" is a retrieval-and-assembly job, not a property of the model.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
